Mony Real Estate Investors Trust saidits investment portfolio consists of 137.1 mln dlrs ofmortgages with an average maturity of less than six years, 43.7mln dlrs of real estate equities and 2.7 mln dlrs of foreclosedreal estate.    The trust's exposure to oil-dependent regions is limited to2.2 mln dlrs, it said.     It said it accepted an offer to sell foreclosed propertyand increased its loss reserve by 750,000 dlrs in anticipationof the sale. Reuter&#3;